{"tid":1213821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩前線嗰啲勇武唔撚好再講啲on9野","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:08:42.000Z","uid":137528,"like":207,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"740f108bad59b23f01edab0003ac1e5d85739dfa","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你,同我講話留番啲物資俾其他人.</span></span><br />\n有冇諗過我地欠左你地幾多野,有冇諗過你地先係最有資格使用物資嘅人.<br />\n<br />\n我自問唔係啲夠膽衝到最前最前幫手整熄的催淚彈嘅人,只係可以幫人走咗先,同上前幫你地沖鹽水<br />\n見住你哋成隻眼紅晒都仲同我地講冇事<br />\n你哋有啲人甚至帶着最普通嘅口罩就衝到最前,你哋知唔知道你哋係香港人嘅最後希望？<br />\n冇咩人可以好似你地咁勇敢.所以如果你哋都受埋傷.香港就冇架喇.<br />\n<br />\n我識一啲20尾打後嘅人同我講話咩<br />\n老喇 唔似你得哋班後生仔可以復上前<br />\n<br />\n但係你哋可唔可以唔好淨係喺天橋上邊叫囂同影相。<br />\n有冇諗過有好多個方法可以幫倒手<br />\n會唔會可以搭的士出去買啲professional 嘅眼罩口罩返嚟<br />\n最少可以令到嗰班企係最前線幫我地保護自己屋企嘅勇士可以喺最低嘅痛苦之下幫手掉返走啲催淚彈或者整熄佢"},{"pid":"5a9a8aa43358f58410330e82d97938ecb43e0b6b","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"仲要今日得咁小人岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490bf7758cef239006491b599b025581b1f4ddf2","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6847c8a28d8f7e8d64316e96770c24167d6d1b6","tid":1213821,"uid":183576,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"啲眼淚停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018d118260f9fd117f05a3c35944d71fd32d2444","tid":1213821,"uid":77542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40d94a428ea00ef7a4680ae056f71495b081f80","tid":1213821,"uid":67905,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁真係仲忍到嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見倒啲鹽水係咁大倒會覺得好浪費可以比更多人"},{"pid":"9d684d803057a8a406b7f11bfefd3ae5ae6ac9a0","tid":1213821,"uid":28152,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"樓主講開啲人話自己老唔衝嗰啲真心燥，我自己都二十尾，但我都同老婆去咗前線守點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味啲人偽善到仆街，真係有心就出嚟啦，有啲阿叔幾十歲都喺前線你廿幾話老？"},{"pid":"78aa71acef5e9e6518532767230423110298b96e","tid":1213821,"uid":147721,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3d98fe0d29c7148a24b5a0f924f4c80614d12","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6847c8a28d8f7e8d64316e96770c24167d6d1b6","tid":1213821,"uid":183576,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"啲眼淚停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"就算未有彈嗰陣都會忍唔住自己喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗 呢個係我地方"},{"pid":"b3e14911c7d6cbafdedf865f33a47b1b3d4527da","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78aa71acef5e9e6518532767230423110298b96e","tid":1213821,"uid":147721,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"講開好想要啲廢老攞個洋蔥喺隻眼度捽一捽 睇吓仲會唔會話係貪玩搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28149dc2ac55b082d100f1a180fd63a884eee4f8","tid":1213821,"uid":221004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"發夢琴日中第一次催淚<br />\n真係眼耳口鼻都痛到慘叫<br />\n<br />\n後尾發覺原來每次後退 <br />\n實有幾位巴絲會幫你沖洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以唔敢企前線嘅人 可以做下洗眼工作 <br />\n至少前線中完 我地可以安心再沖過"},{"pid":"304f4f8f1988ee1fea54dbed6663c78cda28ec15","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d684d803057a8a406b7f11bfefd3ae5ae6ac9a0","tid":1213821,"uid":28152,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"樓主講開啲人話自己老唔衝嗰啲真心燥，我自己都二十尾，但我都同老婆去咗前線守點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味啲人偽善到仆街，真係有心就出嚟啦，有啲阿叔幾十歲都喺前線你廿幾話老？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見倒有啲話自己淨係得錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係淨係買幾個口罩黎就算"},{"pid":"2ee544d0867dc40d8b63632100e140e3eccb7457","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5d5fbb1b289276bf85a7f241f3c8ba86a1f118","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97947810e2d9b9240353e83d30f28bd871813e1e","tid":1213821,"uid":137528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a3fcc66898320c4eaf1786c848f1db16d43de2","tid":1213821,"uid":130190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"304f4f8f1988ee1fea54dbed6663c78cda28ec15","tid":1213821,"uid":